# Dynamic sitemap — served by Netlify Function (also in netlify.toml for netlify dev).
/sitemap.xml  /.netlify/functions/sitemap  200!

# SPA catch-all — MUST be last. Serves index.html for React Router routes
# (e.g. /fr/blog/my-article) so reloads and direct links don't 404 on the CDN.
# Not forced (no !), so real files (assets, robots.txt, favicons) still win.
# NOTE: netlify.toml [[context.production.redirects]] is silently IGNORED by
# Netlify — redirects cannot be scoped to deploy contexts. This file is the
# only place the catch-all works.
/*  /index.html  200
